OL,3,CTwo young children die in house fire
OL,4,Cin Wolverhampton
OL,6,FTwo young children have died in a
OL,7,Fhouse fire in Wolverhampton.
OL,9,FOfficers were called to Mason Street
OL,10,Fat about 8.30pm on Friday along with
OL,11,Fthe West Midlands Fire Service and
OL,12,FWest Midlands Ambulance Service, West
OL,13,FMidlands Police said.
OL,15,FFirefighters entered the property and
OL,16,Frescued two young children but they
OL,17,Fwere pronounced dead at the scene,
OL,18,Fpolice said.
