OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTwo other children and a woman were
OL,12,Falready out of the house before
OL,13,Femergency services arrived.
OL,15,FThey were checked over by ambulance
OL,16,Fstaff but did not need hospital
OL,17,Ftreatment.
